    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Knowledge\" title=\"Knowledge\">Knowledge</a> * <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a> * GAFS</b>\n</p><p><b>GAFS</b>, (Guido Antonelli Finali di Scacchi)<br />\na chess endgame tablebase generator by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Guido_Antonelli&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Guido Antonelli (page does not exist)\">Guido Antonelli</a> for six and more pieces with a <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">command line interface</a> running under <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a>, \nfirst released in June 2006 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nTo use the generated TBs in a chess engine, a library (gafslib.o) is provided for <a href=\"/Unix\" title=\"Unix\">Unix</a>/Linux and <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows 32</a>, \nwith two entry points, initialization and probing <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=GAFS&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/FinalGen\" title=\"FinalGen\">FinalGen</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Freezer\" title=\"Freezer\">Freezer</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=GAFS&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=552&amp;p=5602#p5602\">Re: tbgen compiled!</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Guido_Antonelli&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Guido Antonelli (page does not exist)\">Guido Antonelli</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, June 21, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=1089&amp;p=9910\">A new version of my EGTB generator</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Guido_Antonelli&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Guido Antonelli (page does not exist)\">Guido Antonelli</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, October 25, 2006</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=GAFS&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://users.libero.it/rigel_g/#Inglese\">Program gafs (Guido Antonelli Finali di Scacchi)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://users.libero.it/rigel_g/gafslib1.11.eng\">gafslib1.11.eng</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=GAFS&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=552&amp;p=5602#p5602\">Re: tbgen compiled!</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Guido_Antonelli&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Guido Antonelli (page does not exist)\">Guido Antonelli</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, June 21, 2006</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://users.libero.it/rigel_g/gafslib1.11.eng\">gafslib1.11.eng</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301154610\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 47/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 102/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in p